<HEAD>Quotes From The Presidential Campaign Trail</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are some of the latest comments from the
presidential campaign trail:
   
   GEORGE BUSH, commenting on the so-called gender gap _ the
indication in polls that women voters support Dukakis by a far
highter percentage than do men: ``I am confident we can overcome
this gender gap. I want to be sure I'm as sensitive as possible to
the concerns of these activist women in our party. I think we've
