in the truth. The matter of the vice presidency is a serious
matter.''
   
   FRANK J. FAHRENKOPF Jr., Republican party chairman, saying the
presence of Ohio Sen. John Glenn on the Democratic ticket would
make the GOP's job harder in November: ``He is a national hero.
People take a lot of pride in that and it can transcend party
affiliations.''
